I will be the first to object.

19
00:01:14,020 --> 00:01:14,820
How dare you!

20
00:01:15,300 --> 00:01:15,620
You...

21
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:16,300
Wan'er,

22
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:18,820
I don't blame you

23
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:19,820
