26
00:01:26,620 --> 00:01:27,420
You come back here.

27
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:30,140
You insolent brat.

28
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:33,860
Um...

29
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:34,820
Mr. Wang,

30
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:37,940
let me

31
00:01:39,620 --> 00:01:41,220
offer this tea.

32
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:53,580
Since it is Miss Liu's own wish,

33
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,580
I offer this tea

34
00:01:58,820 --> 00:02:00,380
to you, Madam.

35
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:06,420
Madam,

36
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:24,340
when we met at The Paramount,

37
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:26,820
you told me

38
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,540
you drifted through life,

39
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:29,980
struggling to survive,

40
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,380
and sought someone to rely on.

41
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:35,020
You've gotten this far
in just a few months.

42
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:36,740
Tell me,

43
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:40,580
should I offer my congratulations?

44
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:49,620
Of course, you should.

45
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,700
Marrying Mr. Wang is

46
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:56,780
my heartfelt wish.

47
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:58,220
With this cup of tea,

48
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:00,980
I wish Marshal Chen and Miss Wang

49
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:03,220
a lifetime of happiness.

50
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:12,220
Good.

51
00:03:14,420 --> 00:03:15,220
Good.

52
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:16,420
Rumeng.

53
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:17,780
Well, this matter

54
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:19,340
is settled.

55
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,100
In a couple of days,

56
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,860
we will hold the weddings together.

57
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:25,420
Why don't you go back
to The Paramount now

58
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:27,940
and pack your things?

59
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:30,380
Move in today. How about that?

60
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:32,940
Okay.

61
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:35,460
Come, I will show you to your room.

62
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,420
Let's go.

63
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,260
Mr. Wang.

64
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:43,100
My father will be returning
to Song City shortly.

65
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,740
The Marshal's residence is
undergoing renovations.

66
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:47,420
May I stay at your residence
for a few days?

67
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:50,700
Consider it...

68
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:54,340
An opportunity to spend more time
with Wan'er.

69
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:57,140
No problem at all.

70
00:03:58,580 --> 00:03:59,820
We'd be delighted.

71
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:18,020
[Dock Transfer Contract]
This dowry from Liu Rumeng

72
