73
00:04:22,780 --> 00:04:25,740
From now on,
all shipments will use this dock.

74
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:26,420
Understood.

75
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:28,100
Also...

76
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:31,420
Keep a close watch on Liu Rumeng for me.

77
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:32,620
And on Chen Wenbin.

78
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,100
Is that clear?

79
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:35,100
Yes, sir.

80
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:42,020
Last time, if I hadn't
secretly switched the goods,

81
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:44,180
I might have been caught red-handed

82
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:45,740
by my dear future son-in-law.

83
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:51,940
Is there anything else?

84
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:54,580
No, sir.

85
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:04,220
Wenbin,

86
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,980
are you truly here for a woman,

87
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:10,420
or do you know about my opium trade?

88
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:13,420
Since you dare to move into my house,

89
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:16,820
don't blame me for uncovering the truth.

90
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:30,320
[Memory of Lin Wenruo, Lin Qingyi]

91
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:38,140
Rumeng,

92
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:40,100
kneel before your parents.

93
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:53,140
Why did you take it upon yourself

94
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:54,780
to marry Wang Penghui?

95
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:57,220
Do you still remember the promises
you made to me?

96
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:58,660
I remember.

97
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,180
Never touch opium.

98
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:04,260
Never act alone.

99
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,540
Never risk my life.

100
00:06:07,020 --> 00:06:07,900
Hua, you have to believe me.

101
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:09,700
Marrying Wang Penghui is just a facade.

102
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:11,540
He was already starting to suspect me.

103
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:13,540
If I don't marry into the Wang family,

104
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:14,820
I can never get my revenge.

105
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:17,140
Rumeng, you're still lying to me,
aren't you?

106
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:21,420
Is this because of Chen Wenbin?

107
00:06:26,340 --> 00:06:27,540
I recognized him.

108
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:31,780
He's Su Jinmo from the orphanage.

109
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,820
We only had each other growing up.

110
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,060
I didn't tell him then,

111
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:37,540
and I won't tell him now.

112
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:39,740
I understand
you don't want him involved.

113
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:41,100
But do you really think

114
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:42,540
this will stop Chen Wenbin?

115
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:43,620
The vengeance belongs to the Lin family.

116
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:44,980
It has nothing to do with him.

117
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:48,700
Marrying into the Wang family

118
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:50,740
is a dangerous move,

119
00:06:52,580 --> 00:06:53,820
but it will prove useful.

120
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:26,260
Concubine Liu,

121
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,740
with the floor covered
in broken porcelain like this,

122
00:07:29,140 --> 00:07:30,620
you're still willing to walk on it?

123
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:32,380
Aren't you afraid

124
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:35,380
these shards might cut your feet?

125
00:08:04,780 --> 00:08:06,060
Obstacles in my path.

126
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:08,700
I just crush them and kick them aside.

127
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:11,420
Since I stepped through
the Wang residence's door,

128
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:13,660
I've never been afraid of bleeding.

129
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:16,220
It's you, Miss Wang,
whom I'm concerned about.

130
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,060
From now on,

131
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:20,980
you must learn to properly respect me.

132
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,300
- You...
- Stop!

133
00:08:29,340 --> 00:08:30,100
Wang Wan'er,

134
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:32,180
the Chen family values decorum
above all.

135
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:34,060
Wilful rudeness

136
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:35,380
and disrespect toward one's...

137
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:39,220
elders

138
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,620
will not be tolerated again.

139
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:06,660
I'm your mother-in-law.

140
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:58,460
Qingmao?

141
00:09:58,980 --> 00:09:59,780
Impossible.

142
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:01,860
Impossible! Impossible!

143
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:03,220
You're dead!

144
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:04,500
You can't be here!

145
00:10:04,660 --> 00:10:06,180
You can't be!

146
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:15,380
Wan'er,

147
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:18,380
my dear "friend."

148
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:20,620
Why did you help your father

149
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,780
frame our family for opium trafficking?

150
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,100
It wasn't me! It wasn't me!

151
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:24,100
A huge fire

152
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,860
killed thirteen members of my family.

153
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:26,900
Why?

154
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:27,620
It wasn't me!

155
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:29,020
And you threw me into the sea!

156
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:29,980
It wasn't me!

157
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:31,860
Why?

158
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:46,860
Because your Lin family was stupid!

159
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,620
So what if
we used your Lin family's accounts

160
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:50,980
to smuggle opium?

161
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:54,100
My Dad said he'd pay you!

162
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:55,540
You were the ones who refused!

163
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:56,820
You even had to go to the police!

164
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:57,780
If you didn't die,

165
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:00,620
did you expect me and my Dad
to die instead?

166
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:06,740
And you!

167
00:11:06,780 --> 00:11:07,860
Lin Qingyi!

168
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:11,060
Why were you the beloved,
pampered young miss,

169
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,220
while I was

170
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:15,860
the study maid,
even my own father despised?

171
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:19,460
I hate you! I hate you!

172
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:22,420
The day of the Lin family fire,

173
00:11:22,580 --> 00:11:24,860
I was the one who splashed the oil
on your face!

174
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,860
I wanted to watch you

175
00:11:30,620 --> 00:11:32,220
become an ugly freak

176
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:35,380
that everyone would reject!

177
00:11:43,580 --> 00:11:45,660
Wang Wan'er! Wang Penghui!

178
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:48,580
I won't let you die so easily.

179
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:50,980
I will make you

180
00:11:50,980 --> 00:11:53,340
confess the truth with your own mouths!

181
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:08,740
Qingmao,

182
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:11,420
I searched for you for seven years,

183
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:12,660
never knowing

184
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:15,020
you were carrying such a bloody,
deep-seated hatred.

185
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:17,820
In the past, I failed to keep

186
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:19,220
our promise from the orphanage.

187
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:21,100
Today,

188
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:23,220
let me stay in the Wang family

189
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,500
and get revenge for you.

190
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:29,100
What are you causing a scene about
in the middle of the night...

191
00:12:35,140 --> 00:12:35,940
Help her up.

192
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:40,820
Miss Wang, wake up!

193
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:49,860
What are you shouting for?

194
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:51,900
Look at the state you're in!

195
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:53,180
Dad! Dad!

196
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:54,260
I saw Qingmao!

197
00:12:54,260 --> 00:12:55,420
Qingmao came for me!

198
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:56,860
- Qingmao came for me!
- Nonsense!

199
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,340
No, Dad!

200
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,780
She really came for me!

201
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,020
Get a grip!

202
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:05,460
Dad...

203
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:11,140
Dad! She came for me!

204
00:13:18,180 --> 00:13:19,580
Qingmao came for me!

205
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:20,700
Qingmao came for me!

206
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:21,780
Get back to bed and go to sleep!

207
00:13:22,060 --> 00:13:23,620
Qingmao came for me!

208
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:25,780
Qingmao came for me!

209
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:30,020
The timing is rather convenient.

210
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:32,580
How is it that Qingmao appears now,

211
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:35,820
